title: Does the Samsung Galaxy Book 2 Pro support 5G?
content:
Samsung recently announced the Galaxy Book 2 Pro family of Windows laptops, and it’s packing a few improvements, specifically upgrading to intel’s 12th-generation P-series processors. We were big fans of the Galaxy Book Pro 360 5G last year, but does the Galaxy Book Pro 2 also come with 5G support? Well, yes and no, depending

The post Does the Samsung Galaxy Book 2 Pro support 5G? appeared first on xda-developers.
description: Samsung's Galaxy Book 2 Pro series looks promising, but 5G support will depend on where you live. Users in the US may need to look elsewhere.
